sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as POST /memory
    participant Falkor as FalkorDB
    participant EQ as enrichment_queue
    participant EmQ as embedding_queue
    
    Client->>API: POST /memory
    API->>Falkor: MERGE Memory node
    Falkor-->>API: memory_id
    
    par Background Enqueue
        API->>EQ: enqueue(memory_id, attempt=0)
        API->>EmQ: enqueue(memory_id)
    end
    
    API-->>Client: 201 Created {memory_id, enrichment: "queued"}
    
    Note over Client,EmQ: API returns immediately;<br/>background processing begins